  "detailed_description": "<strong>Pushing the limit</strong> - a game in which you have to show your willpower.<br>Your task is to get to the finish line as quickly as possible, passing obstacles.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >On the track you will meet obstacles:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>-Guns<br></li><li>-Objects that knock you down<br></li><li>-traps<br></li><li>-Many more</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>We put our soul into this project and will try to evoke different emotions in you.<br></li><li>Difficult track, unusual physics - that's what you will find in the game.</li></ul><br><strong>Good luck, fighter!</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Pushing the limit</strong> - a game in which you have to show your willpower.<br>Your task is to get to the finish line as quickly as possible, passing obstacles.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >On the track you will meet obstacles:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>-Guns<br></li><li>-Objects that knock you down<br></li><li>-traps<br></li><li>-Many more</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>We put our soul into this project and will try to evoke different emotions in you.<br></li><li>Difficult track, unusual physics - that's what you will find in the game.</li></ul><br><strong>Good luck, fighter!</strong>",
